high_descs: Walk to the opposite side of the island and face the counter with your back to the island.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Walk to the sink on the opposite side of the room.
Walk to the microwave on the opposite side of the room.
Put the bowl of water into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl of water in the microwave.

high_descs: Head around the island to the right and move to the counter near the white bowl.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Turn left and bring the bowl to the sink.
Fill the bowl with water in the sink.
Move around the island to the right and bring the bowl to the microwave on the counter.
Put the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl filled with water in the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight, then turn right to go around the kitchen island, then go straight, then turn right, then turn left to face the counter near the mirror.
Pick up the bowl on the counter, to the right of the bread.
Turn left, then turn left, then turn left again, then turn right to face the sink.
Wash the bowl in the sink.
Turn right, then turn right, then go straight, then turn right, then go straight, then turn left to face the microwave.
Place the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bowl in the microwave.
